Greek Securities Regulator to Appoint New Head, To Vima Reports

-- B y   M a r c u s   B e n s a s s o n
-- 
2011-10-10T06:56:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/greek-securities-regulator-to-appoint-new-head-to-vima-reports.html
The Hellenic Capital Markets
Commission will appoint Costas Botopoulos as its new head, To
Vima reported, without saying how it got the information.  Botopoulos, a former member of the European parliament,
will replace Anastasios Gavrielides, who resigned last month,
the Athens-based newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
